name: VMJ 6/6: Unfinished (Dec 26)
description:
The last attempt, failed. Made 6 games out of 9. Not sure if I should post this: it's not my art, it's ptoing's! There's really not much of a game here yet tho. It's even less than VMJ 2/6.

At the end of 2012, I tried to make 9 games. This was one of them.
